                "marginLeft": "50px",
                "marginRight": "50px",
                "title": "Welcome to Babylon.js 4.1",
                "desc": "Our mission is to create one of the most powerful, beautiful, and simple Web rendering engines in the world. Our passion is to make it completely open and free for everyone. Up to 3 times smaller and 12% faster, Babylon.js 4.1 includes countless performance optimizations,  continuing the lineage of a high-performance engine. With the new Node Material Editor, a truly cross-platform development experience with Babylon Native, Cascaded Shadows, Navigation Mesh, updated WebXR and glTF support, and much much more, Babylon.js 4.1 brings even more power to your web development toolbox."
            }
        },
